##  Key Formulas & Quick Reference

### Communication Formula

| Formula | Purpose |
|:--------|:--------|
| **Channels = n(n-1)/2** | Calculate communication complexity |

### Quick Decision Guide

| Situation | Best Method |
|:----------|:------------|
| Complex or sensitive topic | Interactive (meeting, video) |
| Simple update | Push (email, report) |
| Reference material | Pull (wiki, shared drive) |
| Urgent matter | Interactive (phone, video) |
| Large audience | Push + Pull (email + intranet) |
| Need audit trail | Formal written |
| Relationship building | Informal interactive |



